item.title: Project1 SDS348
item.description: Introduction The first dataset contains income and poverty data by county for all counties in Texas. It contains the variables: Counties, Per Capita Income, Median Household Income, and % of Population in Poverty. The second dataset contains data about the level of education and employment by county and contains the variables: Counties, % High School Graduate or Higher, % Bachelor s Degree or Higher, and Unemployment Rate (%). The third dataset contains data on opioid-related emergency department visits in 2017 by county.
